description.narrative: The development objective of the project is to improve the protection of property and safety of people from flood events and bring about sustainable utilization of land and water resources within Xining Municipality. The PDO is to be achieved through the provision of (a) a greater level of flood protection and enhanced flood management; (b) improved wastewater collection; (c) improved soil and water conservation of catchments; and (d) institutional strengthening and capacity building in Xining Municipality.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA Artical III Clause 3.01 | Description :The Borrower shall cause the Project to be carried out by the ProjectImplementing Entity in accordance with the provisio ns of Arti cle V of the General Conditions and the Project Agreement. |Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA - Article II, Clause 2.01 | Description :The Project Implementing Entity declares its commitment to theobjectives of the Project and shall provide as needed the funds, faci lities, and other resources required for the Project |Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA - Section I, Paragraph 2 | Description :Qinghai shall cause Xining Municipality to implement or cause to beimplemented the FMM, EMP, RAP, EMDP, and PMP all in a manner and substance satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA - Section I, Paragraph 6 | Description :Implementing Agency shall furnish to the Bank by November 30 eachyear Annual Implementation Plan summarizing the progres s and theProject activities to be undertaken for the following year. |Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA- Schedule, Section I, Paragraph 1 | Description :Qinghai shall cause Xining Municipality to maintain XPLG,XPCO, XPMO, EP, CPLGs, CPCOs, and CPMOs for cordinating and imp lementingthe Project. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA- Schedule, Section II, paragraph A.1 | Description :Implementing Agency shall monitor and evalute theprogress of the Project and prepare Project Reports covering the period of one sem ester and furnished to the Bank by Februar 15and August 15 | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :PA- Schedule, Section III | Description :All goods, works and services required for the Project and to befinanced out of the Loan shall be procured in accordance with the p rovisions of Section III of Schedule 2 to the Loan Agreement. |Frequency :Quarterly
